latestPosts.caption:
If you love blankety lipstick from @maccosmetics then you need to try modesty to 💕 

I love modesty as I find it’s just a shade darker than blankety but still that lovely neutral pink shade

I’ve paired it with 
• cool spice lipliner first 
• chestnut lipliner for definition 
• behaved lipglass air (literally blankety in a lipglass) LOVE 
• 219sh brush to soften the liners 
💕 

Have you tried modesty? I think it’s a underrated lip shade at mac 🥰

Vintage mint meets gothic in the aquatic 🐠 💚 🖤 

I wasn’t going to post this as once I got it onto my laptop I wasn’t that overly impressed with it but, the more I look at it the more I love the colours together and the glossy shine lipglass gives, I can pin point the things I want to change about it and make it better but if we don’t post our not so best work how will we know if we’ve improved? Moral of that point is I’m going to try this again maybe in some months time or next year and compare it to this and see if I’ve improved as an artist trying these editorial and not so pretty/every day wearing looks 💚
